projects.title: Personal Website
projects.bodyText:
- Developer Portfolio Website made in React 
 - Dark Mode Support

projects.title: Sudoku AI Solver
projects.bodyText:
- A Sudoku Solver made in React using **CSP** algorithm. 
 - Option to solve the board using **AI**.
 - Have multiple difficulty levels.

projects.title: Data Analysis of NYC Taxi Dataset
projects.bodyText:
- A Comprehensive Data Analysis of the NYC Taxi Dataset.
 - Analysis includes **Data Cleaning**, **Exploratory Data Analysis**, **Data Visualization** and **Predictive Modelling** (XG Boost, Neural Networks, and Random Forest).

projects.title: Juve
projects.bodyText:
- HackHarvard Project 
 - A Web Application that helps users to do rehabilitation exercises using **Fruit Ninja** using **OpenCV** pose detection of camera videos.

projects.title: Wordle
projects.bodyText: - A replica of New York Times Wordle game with 6-letter words.

projects.title: CIS5210 Artifical Intelligence
projects.bodyText:
- Assignments for CIS5210 Artificial Intelligence 
 - Includes **Search Algorithms**, **Constraint Satisfaction Problems**, **Bayesian Networks**, **Hidden Markov Models**, **Reinforcement Learning**, **Natural Language Processing**, and **Neural Networks**.

projects.title: CIS 5450 Big Data Analytics
projects.bodyText:
- Assignments for CIS 5450 Big Data Analytics 
 - Includes **Data Wrangling**, **Data Visualization**, **Data Modelling**, **Querying**, **Cluster Analysis**, and **Neural Networks**.

projects.title: CIS 1210 Data Structures and Algorithms
projects.bodyText:
- Assignments for CIS 1210 Data Structure and Algorithms 
 - Includes implementations of **Huffman Algorithm**, **Binary Min Heap**, **Graph Algorithms**, **HashMap**.

projects.title: AdMix

projects.title: Events At Penn
projects.bodyText:
- Associated with Penn Spark 
 - A Web Application that helps students to find social events happening at Penn.

projects.title: Instagram Duplicate
projects.bodyText:
- Final Project for NETS 2120 Scalable and Cloud Computing 
 - A Web Application that replicates the functionalities of Instagram with full-stack develepment, databases, and AI.

projects.title: SecTix
projects.bodyText:
- Final Project for CIS 5120 Introduction to Human-Computer Interaction 
 - A Web Application that helps users to buy and sell second-hand tickets for events.

projects.title: Final Project for CIS 5500 Databases And Information Systems
projects.bodyText: - A Web Application that integrates with SQL databases of at least two large datasets.
